snippet.title: Widget Inc. - First Ten Minutes
snippet.description:
Thinking of trying the game out? Here's an unedited gameplay video of the first ten minutes of the game to get you acquainted with the mechanics you'll encounter in the beginning. 

Of course, that's just the start. The free demo adds two more tiers of technology on top of this, with crafting recipes of increasing complexity. And even that's just the start!

Download the demo today - free on Steam!
http://s.team/a/3184110
